TextEng: Who are you?
I want to ask you some questions.
Who you be?
Me have questions.
Goodbye.
My name is <FirstName>.
My name is <FullName>. I'm pleased to meet you.
You don't need to know my name.
I don't usually share my name with cretins.
Me name be <FirstName>.
Me be called <FullName>. Nice meet you.
You not need know name.
You grumpy. Me not tell.
What's put you in this mood?
You're certainly miserable.
Why you in such bad mood?
Why you got stick up butt?
You don't think the ruins exist?
You no think there be ruins?
You're miserable. I'm done talking to you.
Text: 너무 우울하네. 더 이상 얘기 안 해.

TextEng: You too grumpy. Me no talk no more.
Text: 너 너무 심술쟁이. 나 이제 말 안 해.

TextEng: Nothing?
I have no idea.
Me not know.
Oh, I'm sorry. That's horrible.
Guess you should have been paying better attention.
Me sorry. That bad to happen to you brother.
Text: 나... 미안해. 동생한테 나쁜 일 일어났네.

TextEng: Ha! That be funny to see.
What would you be willing to pay to have these trolls and ogres wiped out?
Text: 트롤이랑 오우거 다 쓸어버리면 얼마 줄 거야?

TextEng: That sounds like an important job. I'll do it.
What's your name?
Why are you in such a bad mood?
What you name?
What happen 'round here?
What's going on around here?
Why you bad mood?
What exactly can't you stand?
What you no stand?
What you pay me kill trolls 'n' ogres?
Text: 나한테... 트롤이랑 오우거 죽이면 뭐 줄 거야?

TextEng: Me like kill trolls. Me do job.
Text: 나 트롤 죽이는 거 좋아. 내가 할게.

TextEng: I'm not interested. Goodbye.
Me no want that job. Bye bye.
Text: 나 그거 안 해. 잘 가.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I think it would be a sign of good faith if you fronted me some of that gold.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 선금 좀 주면 서로 믿음이 가지 않겠어?

TextEng: All right, I'm off.
Me want some gold now, else me make you troll-bait.
Text: 나 지금 돈 줘, 아니면 트롤 밥으로 만들어.

TextEng: You better give me some of that gold right now, or else I'll take you with me for bait.
Text: 지금 당장 돈 좀 주는 게 좋을 거야, 아니면 미끼로 끌고 갈 테니까.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me think me should have some gold now, please?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 지금... 돈 좀 주면 안 돼?

TextEng: Me go kill trolls now.
What do you want done again?
I have the troll's head right here.
I've changed my mind, I'll hunt the trolls for you.
No. I'm still not interested.
What you want again?
I have big ugly's head here.
Text: 큰 못생긴 거 머리... 여기 있어.

TextEng: Me want hunt trolls now.
Me not want job still.
The whole thing.
A summary.
I need no reward. Avenging a life and slaying evil is reward enough.
Text: 보상은 필요 없어. 원수를 갚고 악당을 처치한 것만으로 됐어.

TextEng: As we agreed, that will be fine.
You had better find some more, or I'll make you look like this troll.
Text: 더 찾아오는 게 좋을 거야, 아니면 이 트롤처럼 만들어 줄 테니까.

TextEng: No pay. I glad I avenge brother and kill trolls.
Text: 돈 안 받아. 동생 복수하고 트롤 죽여서 기뻐.

TextEng: That be good.
You pay more, or me cut your head off too.
Text: 더 줘, 아니면 너 머리도 잘라.

TextEng: What was I supposed to do again?
I'm working on it.
What me do again?
Me trying. Just wait.
Sure.
No thanks.
